nodes.title: Instructions
widgets_values:
## How to Use

1. Update the text you want AI to read in `Text to Read` box.

2. Read and record the sample text in `Sample Text to Record` box. 

3. All done! Enjoy your own cloned voice in opened Audio Web Viewer page :)

## ComfyUI Custome Nodes

- ComfyUI-F5-TTS
  - see https://github.com/niknah/ComfyUI-F5-TTS
